{"tid":1768433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑係咪又炒左車？","createTime":"2019-12-04T05:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T06:08:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7049b6cc98f5b91e033768d63d12dd492e1aa0cb","tid":1768433,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"美國紐約的明鏡與我華語訪談，上星期五言及引述香港電台「自由風」節目中，香港立法會議員田北辰講：香港有億萬富翁乘私人飛機去美國，在機場被阻撓三小時。而此富豪並非與政治有關聯或知名人士。<br />\n<br />\n此後引起大陸網絡等各方揣測富翁身份，並有傳媒揣測為香港星島報業主席何柱國。<br />\n<br />\n據本人確知：此位人士絕對不是何柱國先生，亦非香港傳媒慣見之本地公眾人物，他在三小時後獲准入境，而且此事發生在孟晚秋事件後之一年內，在國會通過香港人權民主法案之前，與法案制裁無關。<br />\n<br />\n謹此澄清。本人不知道當事人身份，並籲請社會輿論維持人心穩定，不必捕風捉影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3244585428947291/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F3244585428947291%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5563d279\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3244585428947291/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"6010eb8f5db6d1c281fc982cb0eef5b1d779c668","tid":1768433,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"(twitter要人）意大利議會 外務委員會 支持香港, 要求歐盟調查香港警暴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768418</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb0e2af38eb1fb57e83eb2910266591b449007f8","tid":1768433,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">日程表</span></span></strong><br />\n－－－－－－<strong><em>和理非合法活動集合</em></strong>－－－－－－</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五 12 &middot; 6 </span><br />\n「吸吸可危」抵禦催淚彈集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/